00:13:48.140 --> 00:13:52.940
framework and get that to work at scale has been something that's been near and dear to my heart,

00:13:52.940 --> 00:13:58.700
really challenging to do, especially since we have things like the Tweedy distribution,

00:13:58.700 --> 00:14:03.099
