00:15:02.780 --> 00:15:09.419
I guess the non-familiar way to look at it is there's two camps. There's this Frequentist camp

00:15:09.419 --> 00:15:14.299
and there's Bayesian camp, which I don't think is true that much anymore, because I think graduate

00:15:14.299 --> 00:15:22.619
statistics programs are pretty much sort of this probabilistic Bayesian framework goes a long way.

00:15:23.419 --> 00:15:28.859
