00:15:28.859 --> 00:15:36.219
Statistical Rethinking, has come back and you see this. And a lot of different non-statisticians

00:15:36.219 --> 00:15:40.619
have picked non-data scientists to pick that up and epidemiology. And it's just the right way to

00:15:41.419 --> 00:15:48.219
